public void deletethatobject(int objectX, int objectY) { 
	ReplaceObject2(objectX, objectY, 6951, -1, 10);
	}

you arnt supposed to have the object coords in the void, you add something like this

public void deleteObject() {
deletethatobject(9999, 9999);
}

and in boolean process or case 121 add

deleteObject();
